refsect1.para:
     Restituisce il nuovo filename temporaneo, o la stringa &null; se fallisce.

      tempnam example


<?php
$tmpfname = tempnam("/tmp", "FOO");

$handle = fopen($tmpfname, "w");
fwrite($handle, "writing to tempfile");
  	fclose($handle);

// do here something

unlink($tmpfname);
?>
